    },
    {
      "end": 48.84000015258789,
      "text": "You know when you walked in the door I lost my mind",
      "start": 44
    },
    {
      "end": 53.220001220703125,
      "text": "Girl you were so beautiful the sun didn't compare",
      "start": 48.84000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 56.47999954223633,
      "text": "How them hips swayed in the air",
      "start": 53.84000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 59.720001220703125,
      "text": "Girl I look at you and see a picture",
      "start": 56.47999954223633
    },
    {
      "end": 61.939998626708984,
      "text": "That I've never seen before",
      "start": 59.720001220703125
    },
    {
      "end": 64.5,
      "text": "Kids running on the floor",
      "start": 62.84000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 66.26000213623047,
      "text": "While we rocked in chairs",
      "start": 64.5
    },
    {
      "end": 69.0199966430664,
      "text": "Wondering who the hell they are",
      "start": 66.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 70.4800033569336,
      "text": "That's right girl",
      "start": 69.0199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 71.87999725341797,
      "text": "Baby it's all me",
      "start": 70.4800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 74.5199966430664,
      "text": "All the fights, all the lies",
      "start": 71.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 78.91999816894531,
      "text": "All the reasons why you couldn't sleep tonight",
      "start": 74.5199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 83.19999694824219,
      "text": "There's some in the bathroom downstairs",
      "start": 79.5199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 86.86000061035156,
      "text": "Trying to write the right words",
      "start": 83.19999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 90.4800033569336,
      "text": "Well maybe, baby it's all me",
      "start": 86.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 94.16000366210938,
      "text": "Maybe it's all on me",
      "start": 90.4800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 99.31999969482422,
      "text": "Couldn't give you the stability, protection you need",
      "start": 94.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 104.69999694824219,
      "text": "Now baby maybe it's all on me",
      "start": 99.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 110.81999969482422,
      "text": "Now remember when I left that time I went to Alabama State",
      "start": 105.30000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 113.76000213623047,
      "text": "Did some shows there",
      "start": 112.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 115.72000122070312,
      "text": "Told you that the girls weren't great",
      "start": 113.76000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 118.30000305175781,
      "text": "Nothing to look at, nothing like you",
      "start": 115.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 119.26000213623047,
      "text": "Couldn't compare",
      "start": 118.30000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 123.95999908447266,
      "text": "Man girl your hair, your personality",
      "start": 119.9000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 126.23999786376953,
      "text": "Was everything to me",
      "start": 123.95999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 128.52000427246094,
      "text": "Told them little girls to move",
      "start": 126.23999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 130.4600067138672,
      "text": "I'll go play at the fair",
      "start": 128.52000427246094
    },
    {
      "end": 133.6199951171875,
      "text": "Find you a boy that you can treat unfair",
      "start": 130.4600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 136.4600067138672,
      "text": "Cause me I'm waiting for you to get home",
      "start": 134.24000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 139.24000549316406,
      "text": "My girls they're all alone",
      "start": 137.1199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 145.05999755859375,
      "text": "Baby baby you won't throw me away",
      "start": 139.75999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 152.0800018310547,
      "text": "If I say all the right words tonight",
      "start": 147.39999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 153.55999755859375,
      "text": "Now baby maybe",
      "start": 152.0800018310547
    },
    {
      "end": 158.17999267578125,
      "text": "Hey yo let me stay",
      "start": 154.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 161.24000549316406,
      "text": "Cause maybe it's all me",
      "start": 158.3800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 165.22000122070312,
      "text": "All the fights, all the dark in our life",
      "start": 161.24000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 167.0399932861328,
      "text": "It's all me",
      "start": 165.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 172.33999633789062,
      "text": "Best you go run free",
      "start": 168.39999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 176.47999572753906,
      "text": "Cause it's all me",
      "start": 172.4600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 179.82000732421875,
      "text": "It's all on the door",
      "start": 177.17999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 184.74000549316406,
      "text": "Comments on the scribe on the way",
      "start": 181.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 187.32000732421875,
      "text": "All the music in the gym and I",
      "start": 184.74000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 192.16000366210938,
      "text": "Inside the mood we hide in our own vacant eyes",
      "start": 187.32000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 195.82000732421875,
      "text": "Maybe it's all me",
      "start": 193.32000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 202.0800018310547,
      "text": "At least I can look at me that way",
      "start": 196.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 204.6999969482422,
      "text": "Have accountability",
      "start": 202.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 209.86000061035156,
      "text": "Until it truly changes everything about me",
      "start": 204.6999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 212.17999267578125,
      "text": "Girl please come",
      "start": 209.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 214.8800048828125,
